{"tid":2490520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大廚房佬被捕後失聯　遍尋十日無果","createTime":"2021-04-15T15:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T16:43:56.000Z","uid":261647,"like":74,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a324ef3e29384159c9500f2785be0c4f9424a0","tid":2490520,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:57:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WhatsNewsMedia/posts/249194010273392\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhatsNewsMedia%2Fposts%2F249194010273392&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=48dd62c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WhatsNewsMedia/posts/249194010273392</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPGj1Zn8wtq8S4SyMWcf9bKkPpsdQ382Q7JTyn9SFGa4P?filename=HqsC2f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqsC2f8.jpg&h=49153617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：和你報WhatsNewsMedia<br />\n<br />\n[理大廚房佬被捕後失聯<br />\n遍尋十日無果]<br />\n<br />\n人稱理大廚房佬（施景騫），2019年活躍於社會運動人物之一，隨著警方秋後算帳多次被拘捕及控以不同罪行。<br />\n<br />\n本年4月2日晚，廚房佬牽涉旺角太子一宗「在公眾地方打架」被警方再次拘捕，案件交由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。惟當晚被拘捕後，再無人能聯絡上(施)。<br />\n<br />\n事隔十天，社交平台專頁「理大廚房佬酒吧」發表貼文指「暫時已經用盡所有能力。至今仍然未搵到廚房佬身在何方，但是仍會繼續。如有最新消息，會立即通知大家。」<br />\n<br />\n社交平台專頁「理大廚房佬酒吧」管理員曾致電旺角警署查詢，油尖旺區區議員林兆彬亦親身前往赤柱監獄及荔枝角收押所查詢(施)去向，回覆均無此人，亦曾以電子郵件詢問懲教署亦無回覆。有人懷疑廚房佬因社會運動被警方盯上而「被失蹤」。<br />\n<br />\n#理大廚房佬 #施景騫 #失蹤 #被失蹤"},{"pid":"92a19c005b079b6373edf2c2b22cf7b85cfd5d26","tid":2490520,"uid":105691,"like":18,"dislike":8,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf3F4eDsrerkp1Xdj6b7sbST1wZRq45pTM8H5MTFkNoB6?filename=jDWTDHK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDWTDHK.gif&h=19da5e44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32e12ff86d057369f6d2e11b1ad02564f4458dd6","tid":2490520,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"